laboratory_examinations.findings: No polymorphonuclear leukocytes seen. No microorganisms seen. This is a concentrated smear made by cytospin method.
Gallbladder is markedly inflamed, distended and hydropic, measuring up to 17 cm in length, gallbladder wall measures up to 7 mm, and cholelithiasis with a large stone measuring up to 4.3 cm.
